						<summary>

						<p>This seems to be a verse commemorating the victory of the Pāṇḍya king (<hi rend="italic">Teṉṉavar kō</hi>) over a certain Vaḍugeṟinda Magadēśaṉ in battle, in which however he lost his life (<hi rend="italic">Viṭṭaindāṉ</hi>). The writing is of about the 13th century A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
