<lb n="1"/>mālviṭṭa paṭai turantu vaṭu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>keṟinta makatecaṉ vaṭivel vā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṅka kālviṭṭa katirmuṭi melinti 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>raṇaip puṭaittatu muṉ kaṭal poy
<lb n="5"/>vaṟṟa velviṭṭatorutiṟṟu mukiliṭ
